description:
It's been a while since Tommy has fooled around with his buddy Nash. You may recognize him, as he previously went by his middle name Kenny.

If you didn't know, these two guys are best friends and Nash recently showed up here in California to kick back at Tommy's place for a bit.

For this scene, these two hunks are going to blow and go. It's a rainy day out here in the Golden State so TommyD & Kenny decide to get off while waiting for the weather to clear up. Sounds like a plan to us!

Enjoy!
title: Tommy D's Wet Rainy Day
